.TH "xilinx_dma_calc_copysize" 9 "xilinx_dma_calc_copysize" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
xilinx_dma_calc_copysize \- Calculate the amount of data to copy
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" xilinx_dma_calc_copysize
.BI "(struct xilinx_dma_chan *chan "  ","
.BI "int size "  ","
.BI "int done "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "chan" 12
Driver specific DMA channel
.IP "size" 12
Total data that needs to be copied
.IP "done" 12
Amount of data that has been already copied
.SH "RETURN"
Amount of data that has to be copied
